Name: Acatliacapanecatl
Meaning in English: Name or title of a high judge

Name: Acmachquichiuh
Meaning in English: who didn’t do anything? / Who in Heaven's Name Did It? (Nickname)

Name: Acuecucyoticihuati
Meaning in English: Aztec deity of water, rivers, seas, streams, storms, and baptism.

Name: Acxomolciul
Meaning in English: the name of a deity linked to the merchant's deity, Yacateuctli; Seler said that this was another name for Tezcatlipoca

Name: Apozanolotl
Meaning in English: Name of the Aztec goddess of purity

Name: Atlacoya
Meaning in English: Name of Aztec goddess of drought.

Name: Axayacatl
Meaning in English: Son of Tezozomoc, a son of Itzcoatl.

Name: Ayauhteotl
Meaning in English: Name of Aztec goddess of the haze and mist

Name: Cecetzin
Meaning in English: Son of Huanitzin. Installed by the Spanish colonial authorities.

Name: Chalchihuitlcue
Meaning in English: She of the robe of green jewels

Name: Chalmecacihuilt
Meaning in English: Name of Aztec goddess of the underworld.

Name: Chantico
Meaning in English: She who dwells in the house

Name: Cihuacuitlapil
Meaning in English: women's tail, probably a nickname for a young child

Name: Cuallee
Meaning in English: Spelling variation of Cuallea, meaning good.

Name: Cuauhtémoc
Meaning in English: Son of Ahuitzotl, allowed to retain his position as tlatoani by the Spaniards, baptized as Fernando Cuauhtémotzín.

Name: Cuetzpallee
Meaning in English: An alternate spelling for Cuetzpallea. It means lizard.

Name: Epcoatl
Meaning in English: Name is known as a noble name

Name: Guatemoc
Meaning in English: Falling eagle or Descending eagle in Nahuatl. It has many variations, such as Cuathemoc,  Cuauhtemotzin or Guatimozin.

Name: Huanitzin
Meaning in English: Son of Tezozomoctli Acolnahuacatl, a son of Axayacatl. Installed by the Spanish colonial authorities.

Name: Huelitl
Meaning in English: Probably related to wēli “be able to” or wēlik “delicious”

Name: Huetl
Meaning in English: with the n and last i elided.

Name: Ilamatecuhtli
Meaning in English: Name of Aztec fertility and death goddess.

Name: Ilancueitl
Meaning in English: old-woman skirt, first queen of Tenochtitlan

Name: Ilhicamina
Meaning in English: He who shoots arrows at the sky

Name: Miquiz
Meaning in English: death, maybe a day-sign, probably male

Name: Mixcoatlailotlac
Meaning in English: clearly includes the name of the deity mixcoatl

Name: Montezuma
Meaning in English: The archer Lord in an angry state. The last ruler of Aztec

Name: Nacxitl
Meaning in English: This word is of unkown meaning, but probably contains the word ikxitl foot

Name: Namiton
Meaning in English: little spouse, probably a nickname for a child

Name: Nanacacipactzin
Meaning in English: Son of Acamapichtli, a son of Ahuitzotl. Installed by the Spanish colonial authorities. Last tlatoani and last hereditary ruler of Tenochtitlan.

Name: Nochhuetl
Meaning in English: Seems to be related to nochtli cactus fig

Name: Ohtli
Meaning in English: A person who is a champion. Also refereed to the son of Neil.

Name: Olopatzicatl
Meaning in English: olotl is the hard core of the corn cob

Name: Poton
Meaning in English: he stinks (interpreted as abbreviation of potonqui)

Name: Quiauh
Meaning in English: rain, maybe a day-sign name, probably male

Name: Tehuetzquititzin
Meaning in English: Son of Tezcatl Popocatzin, a son of Tizoc. Installed by the Spanish colonial authorities.

Name: Tenan
Meaning in English: I think this is most likely an abbreviation of tenamitl fortification

Name: Tizoc
Meaning in English: Son of Tezozomoc, a son of Itzcoatl.

Name: Tlacuiton
Meaning in English: little taken thing if from tlacuitl something taken

Name: Tlillanhuehue
Meaning in English: old man from the ink place

Name: Tlohui
Meaning in English: Buzzard If related to tlohtli Buzzard

Name: Tochtlee
Meaning in English: Spelling variation of Tochtlea,  meaning rabbit.

Name: Tolnahuacatl
Meaning in English: person from a place close to reeds

Name: Toltecatl
Meaning in English: An artist or a creative person

Name: Tonantzin
Meaning in English: Mother earth or the mother Goddess

Name: Tozi
Meaning in English: Aztec goddess of healing and sweet water

Name: Tupoc
Meaning in English: Spelling variation of Tupack. It means warrior.

Name: Yolyamanitzin
Meaning in English: He who is considerate and just
